{% extends './layouts/layout.njk' %}

{% block pageTitle %}Application successful - {{ serviceName }}{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    {{ govukPanel({
      titleText: "Application successful",
      html: "Your reference number is<br><strong>" + reference + "</strong>"
    }) }}

    <p class="govuk-body">We have sent you a confirmation email that includes all the information about what happens next and what you have to do.</p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What you should do next</h2>

    <p class="govuk-body">Contact the vet to book the review. You'll need to give the vet your reference number.</p>

    <p class="govuk-body">The vet will contact you to organise testing of your livestock. They'll test for:</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>bovine viral diarrhoea (BVD) in dairy and beef cattle</li>
      <li>how effective worming treatments are in sheep</li>
      <li>porcine reproductive and respiratory syndrome (PRRS) in pigs</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="govuk-body">The vet will discuss the test results and treatment options as part of the review.</p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Farm visit</h3>

    <p class="govuk-body">The vet will visit your farm to carry out the review. Discuss with the vet what you want to focus on.</p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Confirm the record and get paid</h3>

    <p>After the vet has recorded information about the review, you'll get an email asking you to confirm the record is correct. Sign in to confirm the record and claim funding for an annual health and welfare review of your livestock </p>
    <p>You'll receive a payment within 28 days.</p>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Get help with your application</h2>

    <p>If you have a question about your application contact the Rural Payments Agency.
      Have your reference with you when you contact us.</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list">
      <li>Telephone: 03000 200 301</li>
      <li>Monday to Friday, 8:30am to 5pm</li>
      <li><a class="govuk-link" href="mailto:ruralpayments@defra.gov.uk">ruralpayments@defra.gov.uk</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="govuk-body"><a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/call-charges">Find out about call charges</a></p>
